155 #if !defined(REG_READ32)
156  #define REG_READ32(address) (*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))
157 #endif
158 
162 #if !defined(REG_WRITE32)
163  #define REG_WRITE32(address, value) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))= (uint32_t)(value))
164 #endif
165 
169 #if !defined(REG_BIT_SET32)
170  #define REG_BIT_SET32(address, mask) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))|= (uint32_t)(mask))
171 #endif
172 
176 #if !defined(REG_BIT_CLEAR32)
177  #define REG_BIT_CLEAR32(address, mask) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))&= ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)(mask))))
178 #endif
179 
184 #if !defined(REG_RMW32)
185  #define REG_RMW32(address, mask, value) (REG_WRITE32((address), ((REG_READ32(address)& ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)(mask))))| ((uint32_t)(value)))))
186 #endif

6050 #define LPIT_TMR_COUNT 4u
6051 
6053 typedef struct {
6054  __I uint32_t VERID;
6055  __I uint32_t PARAM;
6056  __IO uint32_t MCR;
6057  __IO uint32_t MSR;
6058  __IO uint32_t MIER;
6059  __IO uint32_t SETTEN;
6060  __O uint32_t CLRTEN;
6061  uint8_t RESERVED_0[4];
6062  struct { /* offset: 0x20, array step: 0x10 */
6063  __IO uint32_t TVAL;
6064  __I uint32_t CVAL;
6065  __IO uint32_t TCTRL;
6066  uint8_t RESERVED_0[4];
6067  } TMR[LPIT_TMR_COUNT];
6068 } LPIT_Type, *LPIT_MemMapPtr;

6293  uint8_t RESERVED_4[8];
6294  __I uint32_t RSR;
6295  __I uint32_t RDR;
6296 } LPSPI_Type, *LPSPI_MemMapPtr;

7623 #define MPU_EAR_EDR_COUNT 4u
7624 #define MPU_RGD_COUNT 8u
7625 #define MPU_RGDAAC_COUNT 8u
7626 
7628 typedef struct {
7629  __IO uint32_t CESR;
7630  uint8_t RESERVED_0[12];
7631  struct { /* offset: 0x10, array step: 0x8 */
7632  __I uint32_t EAR;
7635  __I uint32_t EDR;
7638  } EAR_EDR[MPU_EAR_EDR_COUNT];
7639  uint8_t RESERVED_1[976];
7640  struct { /* offset: 0x400, array step: 0x10 */
7641  __IO uint32_t WORD0;
7642  __IO uint32_t WORD1;
7643  __IO uint32_t WORD2;
7644  __IO uint32_t WORD3;
7645  } RGD[MPU_RGD_COUNT];
7646  uint8_t RESERVED_2[896];
7647  __IO uint32_t RGDAAC[MPU_RGDAAC_COUNT];
7650 } MPU_Type, *MPU_MemMapPtr;
